{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Tag (タグ)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Tag","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> において、<strong>タグ</strong>は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Element\">要素</a>の作成に使われます。</span>段落を表す <code>&lt;p&gt;</code> のように、HTML の要素の名前が山括弧の中に入ります。なお、終了タグは <code>&lt;/p&gt;</code> のように、名前の前にスラッシュがつきます。そして<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Empty_element\">空要素</a>では終了タグは不要で、付けることもできません。<a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Attribute\">属性</a>が記述されていない場合は、それぞれ既定値が使われます。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"詳細情報","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_knowledge","title":"一般知識","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Wikipedia 上の <a title=\"HTML要素\" href=\"https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/HTML要素\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML要素</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/WHATWG\">WHATWG</a> 上の <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/syntax.html#elements-2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 要素の構文</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"technical_reference","title":"技術リファレンス","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Learn/HTML/Introduction_to_HTML\">HTML 概論</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"詳細情報","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"HTML において、タグは要素の作成に使われます。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Tag","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Tag","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Etiqueta","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Balise","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"태그","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Tag","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Тег","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Tag","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/tag",